{"tid":2410982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新都會廣場優品360刑事損壞案 4人罪成 還押候判","createTime":"2021-02-17T04:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T14:41:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5b2a9894f6afbf3cec5beb31930e572577066d","tid":2410982,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:34:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13686&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=c400ffe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13686</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官 #提堂 <br />\n#1013葵芳 <br />\nD1:陳(17) / D2:曾(17)<br />\nD3: * (15) / D5: *(14)<br />\nD7:黃(18) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：刑事損壞 <br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n各被告同被控於2019年10月13日，在葵涌新都會廣場優品5樓574A號舖優品360內，與一不知名男子損壞屬於彩鷗國際有限公司的財產，意圖摧毀或損壞該財產或罔顧該財產是否會被摧毀或損壞 <br />\n<br />\n同案的D4和D6已較早前在 #羅德泉主任裁判官 席前認罪。<br />\n____________________<br />\n速報：‼️D1,2,3,7 認罪，罪名成立‼️（詳情後補）<br />\n‼️D5亦打算認罪，2月22日處理答辯‼️ <br />\n<br />\n各被告求情詳情後補。 <br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2021年3月10日 在東區裁判法院判刑，D5 押後至2021年2月22日 在西九龍裁判法院兒童法庭答辯。<br />\n<br />\n🛑D1、D2、D3、D7即時還押<br />\n🟢D5維持原有條件保釋"},{"pid":"462449da6048653d5d91f92fe72dfe01d0cc12c8","tid":2410982,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748507acc605a2be10d391e9aa73f4703491ef1a","tid":2410982,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\"